{# content description for Lift-It app #}
<p>Lift-It is a weightlifting-focused web application with a user-friendly interface that helps users create personalised workout routines.</p>
<p>Key features include:</p>
<ul> {# generate list of key features of current project #}
    {% for feature in projects[0].keyFeatures%}
        <li> {{ feature }} </li>
    {% endfor %}
</ul>

<p>For project's technical details and/or my developer growth from its development, click below.</p>
{# dropdown menu, revealProjectText function from main.js displays correct content when clicked #}
<select id="liftIt-select-options">
    <option value="instruct-visitor">Learn more</option>
    <option value="inner-workings">What technologies did I use?</option>
    <option value="technical-experience">Technical experience gained</option>
</select>
<div id="liftIt-technical-experience" style="display:none">
    <h3>Lessons learned</h3>
    <p>Creating a full-stack app offered valuable learning opportunities in key growth areas, including:</p>
    <ul> {# generate list of key experinece gained from completing current project #}
        {% for experience in projects[0].technicalExperienceGained %}
            <li> {{ experience }} </li>
        {% endfor %}
    </ul>
</div>
<div id="liftIt-inner-workings" style="display:none">
    <h3>Technologies used</h3>
    {# generate description of technologies used during current project #}
    {% for technology in projects[0].technologiesUsed %}
        <p> {{ technology }} </p>
    {% endfor %}
</div>